<div class="hero">
  <%= image_tag "banner.jpg", alt: "Tudo Bem Maman", class: "banner" %>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <h1 class="title animate-fade-in-up">TUDO BEM MAMAN</h1>
    <p class="subtitle animate-fade-in-up delay-200">Inspired by phonecalls between a mother and a student who left to study in Lisboa and living his best life</p>
    <p class="animate-fade-in-up delay-300"><%= link_to "SHOP NOW", clothes_path, class: "text-button" %></p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="sect">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="flex">
      <%= image_tag "owner.png", alt: "Inès Rolland", class: "owner" %>
      <div class="comment-ines">
        <h3 class="owner-name">Inès Rolland</h3>
        <div class="first-section"></div>
        <p class="comment-content">Cette marque part d'une aventure familiale entre mon frère et moi qui avons vécu tous les deux au Portugal. <br>Découvre nos dernières créations !</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container collection-section">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6 first-col">
      <h3>Découvrez nos t-shirts d'origine française</h3>
      <p>Conçue à Paris et designé au Portugal, nos t-shirts apportent du soleil dans vos vies</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <%= image_tag "banner-2.jpg", alt: "Collection", width: 600, class: "banner-2 img-responsive" %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="button-home"><%= link_to "VOIR LA COLLECTION", clothes_path, class: "text-button" %></p>
</div>
